divs: Sighting Details1. Went out back to have a cigarette. 2. Looking at stars. 3. Nothing, thought it was just my eyes. 4. Dull black boomerang shaped moving slow from east to west. 5. This has been more than a month ago and I cannot put it out of my mind. 6. Lost sight as it pass the roof of my house.
